parameters: Poso: "Hey! You're the one who came from another place, right?"

Poso: "Man, when you were brought here, I wondered what would happen... but
Umi's healing magic worked wonders, huh?"

Poso: "No, I'm going to say it. You know, Umi has been casting healing
magic on you until she was exhausted every day. That's why you're alive
now."
Umi: "It's not... it wasn't a big deal..."

Poso: "Damn it! I wanted to take her place so badly! She was sweating from
her forehead! I've never seen Umi so desperate!"

Poso: "Well, I knew it! That's the kind of girl Umi is! So make sure you
repay her properly, alright?"
Kru: "Ah. Thanks for telling me. And Umi... thank you, really."
Poso: (Ah, someday I want to distort that face with pleasure...)
Poso: "This has turned into a serious situation."

Poso: "Kru-san... Thank you so much for saving my village... I really
thought... this time it was hopeless."
Poso (But before I die, I want to have a go with Umi!!)

Poso: "Lord Kru! That was an incredible battle! This shop is still here
thanks to you, Lord Kru! Thank you!"
